<LegalLayout title="Privacy Policy" lastUpdated="March 21, 2026">
  <h2>Overview</h2>
  <p>
    SportsOnTV ("we," "us," or "our") operates the SportsOnTV mobile application
    (the "App"). This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in
    connection with your use of the App.
  </p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>
    We do not collect, store, or process any personal information about you. We
    do not require you to create an account or provide any personal details to
    use the App.
  </p>
  <p>
    Your device's operating system and the platform through which you downloaded
    the App (Apple App Store or Google Play Store) may collect certain
    information automatically, such as device identifiers and usage statistics.
    This data is governed by their respective privacy policies:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      Apple: <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      Google: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://policies.google.com/privacy</a>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>
    Since we do not collect personal information, we do not use or share it.
  </p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    The App is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly
    collect personal information from children. If you believe a child has
    provided us with personal information, please contact us and we will
    promptly address it.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time at our sole discretion.
    When we post changes, we will revise the "last updated" date at the top of
    this Privacy Policy. We recommend that you check our Website from time to
    time to inform yourself of any changes in this Privacy Policy or any of our
    other policies.
  </p>

  <h2>Contact Us</h2>
  <p>
    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
    <a href="mailto:legal@sportsontv.app">legal@sportsontv.app</a>
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
